**Describe the bug**
I use the following code to do test.
```
    class Program
    {
        public static void Main()
        {
            string cls_model = "E:\\c_sharp_deploy/cls/solar_cell_cls.onnx";
            string cls_img = "E:\\c_sharp_deploy/cls/test_imgs/10005.png";

            int gpuDeviceId = 0;
            var cls_session = new InferenceSession(cls_model, SessionOptions.MakeSessionOptionWithCudaProvider(gpuDeviceId));

            for (int tt = 0; tt < 60; tt++)
            {
                int aa = Environment.TickCount;
                var cv2_img = cv2.imread(cls_img, IMREAD_COLOR.IMREAD_COLOR);
                var img = np.array(cv2_img).astype(NPTypeCode.Float);
                float[] sys_array = img.ToArray<float>();
                Tensor<float> img_tensor = new DenseTensor<float>(sys_array, new[] { 512, 512, 3 });
           
                var cls_input = new List<NamedOnnxValue> { NamedOnnxValue.CreateFromTensor("input", img_tensor) };
               
                int bb = Environment.TickCount;
                Console.WriteLine($"create input tensor {bb - aa}");
                using IDisposableReadOnlyCollection<DisposableNamedOnnxValue> cls_result = cls_session.Run(cls_input);
                int cc = Environment.TickCount;
                Console.WriteLine($"inference {cc - bb}");
                Console.WriteLine("----------------------------\n");
                Thread.Sleep(20);

            }
        }
    }
```
Inference time keeps the same if I do not use Thread.Sleep() or use sleep time <=50ms after each each inference iteration. 
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/32631344/148628249-2017e8ba-7252-432a-98f3-a4c3d05101a6.png)
If I use Thread.Sleep(500), some inference iteration times become long.
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/32631344/148628356-34c124b4-73cd-40b9-a9ed-54a8058633c5.png)
If I use Thread.Sleep(2000), all the inference times become  quite long.
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/32631344/148629456-5a89a70f-1665-499d-aab1-75ac172da3f1.png)



